replies.body:
Welcome to the Rift! {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}} 

Since you mentioned the recall icon isn't properly displaying on top of not being able to recall whatsoever, it seems to me that some files may have gotten corrupted while you were installing. 

Try running our [Hextech Repair Tool](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/224826367-Automated-Troubleshooting-Hextech-Repair-Tool) and let me know if that fixes it! Also, be sure to do these tests either in a custom game or the training mode.
